data.description: Great starter home located just moments from downtown South Lyon! This home offer 3 bedrooms, 1 1/2 baths. Cute floorplan and full basement, perfect for adding additional family room, office, etc. Fresh paint and new flooring in much of the home- just move right in and make this your own! Two car detached garage and fenced in yard. Conveniently located within walking distance to downtown, this property offers easy access to a variety of amenities. Explore the charming downtown area, which is known for its local shops, boutiques, and restaurants. This home is priced to sell, don't miss out! Open House 4/14 from 1-3. Offers will not be reviewed until Monday, 4/15.
